# 🔧 PHASE 1 — FOUNDATION AUDIT (Firebase + Stripe + Core Architecture)

## 1.1 Firebase Audit
Verify collections:
- users
- profiles
- subscriptions
- auctions
- bids / registrations
- inspections
- dealers
- equipment_listings
- notifications

### Requirements
- Every user → has a profile document created on signup
- Every profile → linked via `userId`
- Subscriptions → tied to `userId`

### Fixes
- Add Cloud Function for profile creation
- Repair orphaned or broken relationships

