## 1.2 Authentication + Roles Audit

### Roles
- member
- owner_operator
- dealer
- pro_dealer
- admin
- super_admin

### Requirements
- Role stored in Firebase Auth + Firestore
- Role-based UI rendering

### Fixes
- Route guards / middleware
- Fix privilege escalation risks

