## 1.3 Stripe Integration Audit

### Verify
- Customer created on signup
- Subscription plans:
  - Member Plans ($0)
  - Owner Operator ($39)
  - Dealer ($499)
  - Pro Dealer ($999)

### Payment Features
- Add payment method
- Remove payment method

